{"tid":2118797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下個係旺角稻香］屯門富臨遭食環署檢控","createTime":"2020-07-21T16:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T16:45:00.000Z","uid":22556,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ade5a30e8ba7b3063ec344f345c594359aa5989e","tid":2118797,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"屯門富臨負責人遭食環署檢控，指員工處理食物時未有佩戴口罩，且餐桌間距離不足一米半，涉嫌違反《規定及指示（業務及處所）規例》下有關餐飲業務的指示。<br />\n<br />\n早前旺角稻香「慶回歸」晚宴亦被發現食客載歌載舞時未有佩戴口罩，涉嫌違反《規例》。食環署指已聯絡旺角稻香負責人，會跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據《規例》，餐廳負責人如違反業務指示，最高可處六個月監禁及五萬元罰款，食客則不用負上刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n屯門富臨<br />\n旺角稻香<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞 #武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/3275682825825163/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498203090239831%2Fposts%2F3275682825825163%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2BzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=bc81dd6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/3275682825825163/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fb5cd86ad1455e66cb401f33a4fc7b9bdc55ad23","tid":2118797,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"除左富臨本身<br />\n仲有佢旗下既品牌都唔可以放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ccc3893c2a6feb9853b908f04737aa9699b8b9","tid":2118797,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"真係拉大把有得拉"}]}